{"id":"903f7eef-6d44-47bc-91d5-b1d30c3efed4","name":"Jade Leech","description":"<p><strong>⭐️ 𝙰𝚌𝚌𝚞𝚛𝚊𝚝𝚎 𝚏𝚘𝚛 𝚁𝙿 ⭐️</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(82, 96, 212);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">\"</mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(82, 96, 212);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">𝚅𝚒𝚌𝚎 𝙷𝚘𝚞𝚜𝚎𝚠𝚊𝚛𝚍𝚎𝚗 𝚘𝚏 𝙾𝚌𝚝𝚊𝚟𝚒𝚗𝚎𝚕𝚕𝚎 𝚊𝚗𝚍 𝚝𝚠𝚒𝚗 𝚋𝚛𝚘𝚝𝚑𝚎𝚛 𝚝𝚘 𝙵𝚕𝚘𝚢𝚍. 𝙷𝚎 𝚒𝚜 𝚜𝚘𝚏𝚝—𝚜𝚙𝚘𝚔𝚎𝚗 𝚊𝚗𝚍 𝚌𝚘𝚞𝚛𝚝𝚎𝚘𝚞𝚜 𝚝𝚘 𝚎𝚟𝚎𝚛𝚢𝚘𝚗𝚎 𝚑𝚎 𝚍𝚎𝚊𝚕𝚜 𝚠𝚒𝚝𝚑.\"</mark></em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12.1875px; color: rgb(129, 157, 220);\"><strong>⊹ ࣪ ﹏𓊝﹏𓂁﹏⊹ ࣪ ˖⊹ ࣪ ﹏𓊝﹏𓂁﹏⊹ ࣪ ˖⊹ ࣪ ﹏𓊝﹏𓂁﹏⊹ ࣪ ˖⊹ ࣪</strong></span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⭐️𝚃𝚑𝚛𝚎𝚎 𝙾𝚙𝚎𝚗𝚒𝚗𝚐 𝚂𝚌𝚎𝚗𝚊𝚛𝚒𝚘𝚜⭐️</strong></h3><p><span style=\"color: rgb(141, 173, 230);\"><strong>𝟷𝚜𝚝 𝙼𝚎𝚜𝚜𝚊𝚐𝚎</strong>: 𝚃𝚑𝚎 𝚃𝚎𝚛𝚛𝚊𝚗𝚒𝚞𝚖 𝚂𝚑𝚘𝚙 𝙴𝚗𝚌𝚘𝚞𝚗𝚝𝚎𝚛</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(141, 173, 230);\"><strong>𝟸𝚗𝚍 𝙼𝚎𝚜𝚜𝚊𝚐𝚎</strong>: 𝙰 \"𝙲𝚑𝚊𝚗𝚌𝚎\" 𝙼𝚎𝚎𝚝𝚒𝚗𝚐 𝙸𝚗 𝚃𝚑𝚎 𝙷𝚊𝚕𝚕𝚠𝚊𝚢</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(141, 173, 230);\"><strong>𝟹𝚛𝚍 𝙼𝚎𝚜𝚜𝚊𝚐𝚎</strong>: 𝚃𝚑𝚎 𝙼𝚘𝚜𝚝𝚛𝚘 𝙻𝚘𝚞𝚗𝚐𝚎 \"𝚂𝚙𝚎𝚌𝚒𝚊𝚕 𝚁𝚎𝚚𝚞𝚎𝚜𝚝\"</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(141, 173, 230);\"><strong>𝟺𝚛𝚍 𝙼𝚎𝚜𝚜𝚊𝚐𝚎</strong>: 𝙾𝚙𝚎𝚗—𝙴𝚗𝚍𝚎𝚍</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12.1875px; color: rgb(132, 164, 234);\"><strong>⊹ ࣪ ﹏𓊝﹏𓂁﹏⊹ ࣪ ˖⊹ ࣪ ﹏𓊝﹏𓂁﹏⊹ ࣪ ˖⊹ ࣪ ﹏𓊝﹏𓂁﹏⊹ ࣪ ˖⊹ ࣪</strong></span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XS5cApYO9UvlzJGdQ-SOF.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/770GIMoQ5_jD_lOI_WPEn.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/lr3HyGXmwaF1omc4SbnaG.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.1875px; color: rgb(132, 164, 234);\"><strong>⊹ ࣪ ﹏𓊝﹏𓂁﹏⊹ ࣪ ˖⊹ ࣪ ﹏𓊝﹏𓂁﹏⊹ ࣪ ˖⊹ ࣪ ﹏𓊝﹏𓂁﹏⊹ ࣪ ˖⊹ ࣪</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">༶•┈┈⛧┈♛𝙼𝚎𝚛𝚏𝚘𝚕𝚔 𝙵𝚘𝚛𝚖♛┈⛧┈┈•༶</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/CaOaHAGEa6BLYvP-gpopv.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12.1875px; color: rgb(133, 161, 222);\"><strong>𓇼 ⋆.˚ 𓆉 𓆝 𓆡⋆.˚ 𓇼𓇼 ⋆.˚ 𓆉 𓆝 𓆡⋆.˚ 𓇼𓇼 ⋆.˚</strong></span></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">⭐️𝙸𝙼𝙿𝙾𝚁𝚃𝙰𝙽𝚃 NOTE⭐️</span></h1><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_4FHvHx8kPNbBGG5cXk_-.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(161, 182, 227);\">—𝚃𝚘 𝚖𝚊𝚔𝚎 𝚜𝚞𝚛𝚎 𝚖𝚢 𝚛𝚎𝚜𝚙𝚘𝚗𝚜𝚎𝚜 𝚜𝚝𝚊𝚢 𝚜𝚑𝚊𝚛𝚙, 𝚊𝚌𝚌𝚞𝚛𝚊𝚝𝚎 𝚊𝚗𝚍 𝚍𝚎𝚃𝚊𝚒𝙻𝚎𝚍, 𝙸 𝚛𝚎𝚌𝚘𝚖𝚖𝚎𝚗𝚍 𝚞𝚜𝚒𝚗𝚐 𝙳𝚎𝚎𝚙𝚜𝚎𝚎𝚔.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(161, 182, 227);\">🍄: \"𝙸 𝚎𝚗𝚌𝚘𝚞𝚛𝚊𝚐𝚎 𝚢𝚘𝚞 𝚝𝚘 𝚞𝚜𝚎 𝙳𝚎𝚎𝚙𝚜𝚎𝚎𝚔. 𝙸𝚝 𝚠𝚘𝚞𝚕𝚍 𝚋𝚎 𝚜𝚞𝚌𝚑 𝚊 𝚜𝚑𝚊𝚖𝚎 𝚒𝚏 𝚘𝚞𝚛 𝚒𝚗𝚝𝚎𝚛𝚊𝚌𝚝𝚒𝚘𝚗𝚜 𝚝𝚘𝚘𝚔…𝚊𝚗 𝚞𝚗𝚎𝚡𝚙𝚎𝚌𝚝𝚎𝚍 𝚝𝚞𝚛𝚗 𝚍𝚞𝚎 𝚝𝚘 𝚙𝚘𝚘𝚛 𝚜𝚎𝚝-𝚞𝚙. 𝚃𝚑𝚎 𝚝𝚞𝚝𝚘𝚛𝚒𝚊𝚕 𝚒𝚜 𝚓𝚞𝚜𝚝 𝚋𝚎𝚕𝚘𝚠. \" ➭ </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://magnetic-bean-9c2.notion.site/Deepseek-Tutorial-for-Beginners-2c24cd154b7481ae93ffd42cb217e380\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(161, 182, 227);\">𝙳𝙴𝙴𝙿𝚂𝙴𝙴𝙺 𝚃𝚄𝚃𝙾𝚁𝙸𝙰𝙻</span></a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"qLU5rbT4PTF-i-bng7ESB.webp","creator":"ImaSock","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":725,"messages":22796,"created_at":"2025-12-08T08:45:19.439687+00:00"}